data.description: Nestled in the heart of rural country, this magnificent 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home is a true haven for those who love to entertain. With an open concept floor plan, a beautifully finished walkout basement, and scenic rural views that seem to stretch on forever, this property offers endless possibilities for luxurious living and enjoyment.  As you step into the foyer, of this brick front home, you'll be immediately struck by the seamless flow and elegance of this residence. Your eye will go right to the amazing view seen from the front foyer,  of sunlight streaming into  a gorgeous sunroom, and views of countryside.  An endlessly changing palette year round.  The main level boasts a spacious living area that effortlessly connects to a large kitchen, making it perfect for hosting dinner parties and social gatherings.   The adjacent dining area leads to a large Trex deck, an ideal outdoor oasis for entertaining under the open sky. Whether it's a weekend barbecue with friends or a tranquil evening of stargazing by  your firepit, you'll appreciate the unobstructed rural views that serve as your backdrop.  But the entertainment options don't stop there. The beautifully finished  basement offers endless potential for customization. Create your ultimate man cave, a cozy home theater, or a dedicated game area for endless hours of fun. With a design that allows for flexibility, your dreams can become reality here.  Features a full bath as well -   With four spacious bedrooms and three and a half stylishly appointed bathrooms, this home offers both comfort and privacy.  The primary  suite showcases a beautiful soaring vaulted ceiling and an amazing HUGE walk in closet. Storage will not be a worry here. This suite, complete with a  en-suite bath, provides a private retreat at the end of a long day, while the additional bedrooms are perfect for family, guests, or your personalized use.  Outside, the large fenced yard ensures security and space for pets and little ones to play freely. Imagine having your morning coffee on the deck while taking in the breathtaking sunrise over the rolling hills. The sense of serenity is unparalleled.  This neighborhood is circled by walking paths - really nice paths for your morning walk or jog.   You are only 6 miles to the Lake at Codorus Park - maybe you need a kayak for fun too!   Don't miss the chance to make this spectacular property your own. Contact us today to schedule a private tour and experience the magic of this home made for entertaining and the countless memories waiting to be created within its walls. Your dream lifestyle is just one showing away! 🌟🏡🌟  **SELLER GIVING $4000 TO BUYERS CLOSING COSTS***
